Example of a 4x4 torus.
In order to make toruses with anysize try using the scripts provided in /samples/network/scripts

Torus without manual routing may lead to cycle in the network and ultimately deadlock. For more information about cycle and deadlock check out multi2sim manual (Interconnection Network Chapter)

Run the following:
/m2s --net-sim net0 --net-config net-torus --net-injection-rate 32 --net-msg-size 144 --net-max-cycles 120 --net-visual net.vis
